title: UDM Hosts Open House at Macomb University Center (University of Detroit Mercy)
text: ( Source : University of Detroit Mercy ) University of Detroit Mercy will host an open house at the Macomb University Center on Thursday, October 15 , 2015 from 4:30-7 p.m. The University offers bachelor and master's degree programs at Macomb
